attr.title: Tales From The Other Side
attr.desc: In Tales From The Other Side, you wake up in an old attic in the "FLYPSIDE", a parallel dimension to ours, centuries ahead in the future of an alternate timeline... With no memories of anything beforehand, you have only one thing on your mind. You need to go back. Back to the abyss below you!
